        <div class="center">
            <Navbar title="papers" />
            <div box-="square" shear-="both">
                <div class="header">
                    <span> <h1>Papers</h1> </span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-container">
                    <div class="flex-item-left">
                        <p>
                            Here is the list of my publications. In case you are
                            interested in my conferences talks, please search
                            the archive page.
                        </p>

                        <br />

                        <p>
                            You can also consult my pages in the indexing
                            systems: <a
                                href="https://scholar.google.it/citations?user=E0nt-XYAAAAJ&hl=en"
                                >Google Scholar</a
